    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 25,
      "options": {
        "content": "**Conversation:** `${conversation_id}`\n\n**What the AI sees** (auto-summarized from spans + logs in this conversation):\n\n1. The chat assistant called the `search_products` tool.\n2. Tool dispatched `GET search-service:3000/?q=mice` — returned **HTTP 500**.\n3. search-service emitted span `db.postgres.query` with status **ERROR**: `failed to query products for category=mice` (Postgres code **42703 / undefined_column**).\n4. The failing SQL referenced a column that doesn't exist in `products` — symptomatic of a **partially-rolled migration** or **stale schema**.\n\n**Suggested next step:** check `search-service` for the column name vs the live `products` table schema. The Span breakdown panel below shows the failing SQL verbatim.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "🤖 AI-assisted diagnosis",
      "transparent": false,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "${datasource_loki}"
      },
      "description": "Live tail of evaluator and diagnosis log lines scoped to this conversation_id. The eval framework auto-classifies tool errors, hallucinations, and policy issues — visible here in real time.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 26,
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "showLabels": false,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "${datasource_loki}"
          },
          "expr": "{namespace=\"observibelity\"} |= \"${conversation_id}\" |~ \"(?i)(evaluator|tool .* returned error|chat done:|sigil generation)\"",
          "queryType": "range",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "🔬 AI investigation feed — eval + diagnosis events for this conversation",
      "type": "logs"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
